          {
            "__typename": "ComponentBlocksDescription",
            "content": "<p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:CircularTT-Book !important;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px 0px 1em;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-shadow:inherit;text-transform:none;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Although the AHS seems like an impregnable fortress in the long run for the mining industry, it still has some challenges. Ineffective haul road maintenance might result in slowing or stopping events of Autonomous Haul Trucks. To improve haul road maintenance, contributing factors to these slow or prevent events must be checked upon:</p><ul style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:CircularTT-Book, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;list-style:none;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:15px;orphans:2;outline:0px;overflow:visible;padding:0px 0px 1em;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-shadow:inherit;text-transform:none;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:inherit;line-height:24px;list-style:disc;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"><p style=\"margin-left:25px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;letter-spacing:inherit;margin:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">Proximity</strong> – Water Truck or Grader operating in the vicinity of autonomous vehicles</p></li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:inherit;line-height:24px;list-style:disc;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"><p style=\"margin-left:25px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;letter-spacing:inherit;margin:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">Loss of Traction</strong> – Over-watering Road leads to vehicles losing traction</p></li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:inherit;line-height:24px;list-style:disc;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"><p style=\"margin-left:25px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;letter-spacing:inherit;margin:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">Rutting</strong> – Poor Road conditions get detected as obstacles by the sensors</p></li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:inherit;line-height:24px;list-style:disc;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"><p style=\"margin-left:25px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;letter-spacing:inherit;margin:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">Dust</strong> – Speed restraints are placed when dust levels are too high.</p></li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:inherit;line-height:24px;list-style:disc;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"><p style=\"margin-left:25px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;letter-spacing:inherit;margin:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">Knock-on effect</strong> – A vehicle stopped behind another that has been affected by either proximity, loss of traction, rutting, or dust</p></li></ul>"
          },
          {
            "__typename": "ComponentBlocksHeading",
            "text": "The Way Forward – Future Road"
          },
          {
            "__typename": "ComponentBlocksDescription",
            "content": "<p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:CircularTT-Book !important;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px 0px 1em;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-shadow:inherit;text-transform:none;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Although the autonomous haul trucks market is not so mature currently, there will be significant <a style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(46, 163, 242);font-family:CircularTT-Book !important;font-style:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:inherit;line-height:1em;margin:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px 0px 10px;text-align:inherit;text-decoration:none;text-shadow:inherit;text-transform:none;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.futurebridge.com/mining-and-construction-equipment/\">technological advancements</a> bringing about a higher level of commercialization in the market.</p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:CircularTT-Book !important;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-shadow:inherit;text-transform:none;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">There are different levels of automation for autonomous vehicles, and the same stands true for autonomous haul truck systems. It has four operations levels: driver assists, remote control, teleoperation, and complete autonomy.</p>"
          },
          {
            "__typename": "ComponentBlocksImagePopup",
            "imagePopupTitle": "autonomous haul truck systems",
            "imagePopup": {
              "width": 1920,
              "height": 1065,
              "url": "https://dev-strapi.futurebridge.com/uploads/Exhibit_6_1_ba9aebacdd.png",
              "previewUrl": null,
              "alternativeText": null
            },
            "enable": true
          },
          {
            "__typename": "ComponentBlocksDescription",
            "content": "<p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:CircularTT-Book !important;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px 0px 1em;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-shadow:inherit;text-transform:none;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Most of the trucks being developed and innovated are primarily aligned to be completely autonomous. The fully autonomous haul trucks would work with the following systems, and the developments in these components would also alleviate the performance of autonomous haulage systems as well:</p><ul style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:CircularTT-Book, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;list-style:none;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:15px;orphans:2;outline:0px;overflow:visible;padding:0px 0px 1em;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-shadow:inherit;text-transform:none;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:inherit;line-height:24px;list-style:disc;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"><p style=\"margin-left:25px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;letter-spacing:inherit;margin:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">Kit Sensors</strong> – A collection of sensors collect the environment and relay it to onboard systems to provide surrounding awareness to the haul trucks. As highly developed sensors with higher sensitivity and intelligence arrive in the marketplace, the haulage systems would function better, and the haul trucks would stop and change at the right time.</p></li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:inherit;line-height:24px;list-style:disc;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"><p style=\"margin-left:25px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;letter-spacing:inherit;margin:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">Control Unit</strong> – It is the brain of the haul truck and the interpreter between the haul truck, server, and the platform the operator uses to relay information. It is the most critical component, and many advancements are being made to improve the trucks’ intelligence. AI is also used along with big data to relay suggestions to the users regarding alternative pathways to the operators. The vehicle operation interface is also getting simpler by the day for the ease of training for the operators.</p></li></ul><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:CircularTT-Book !important;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px 0px 1em;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-shadow:inherit;text-transform:none;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">There is also scope for autonomous haulage trucks in space mining in the far future. When it is easier to transport mining equipment to mine resources in outer space, these trucks will play a huge role there since they require a remote operator and can be used to mine without risk.</p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:CircularTT-Book !important;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-shadow:inherit;text-transform:none;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Optimize your mining operations with our <a style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(46, 163, 242);font-family:CircularTT-Book !important;font-style:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:inherit;line-height:1em;margin:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px 0px 10px;text-align:inherit;text-decoration:none;text-shadow:inherit;text-transform:none;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.futurebridge.com/contact-us/?utm_source=website&amp;utm_medium=article&amp;utm_campaign=industry%2Fperspectives-industrial-manufacturing%2Fautonomous-haulage-systems-the-future-of-mining-operations%2F#business-objective\">expert consulting</a><strong style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;background-color:transparent;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-shadow:none;box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;letter-spacing:inherit;margin:0px;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:inherit;text-shadow:inherit;transition:none;vertical-align:baseline;\" data-start=\"3\" data-end=\"62\">.</strong> From sustainability to efficiency, unlock data-driven insights and innovative strategies for a smarter, more responsible future.</p>"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
